This past year I was honored to present the award for the Most Impactful Game of 2016. And that award went to a truly beautiful, soulful, and heart-wrenching experience titled THAT DRAGON, CANCER. Steph and I are eager to go through that experience with you in this episode. Join us for one of the realest GT Live episodes yet, and prepare for an emotional hurricane.
